Global Self-Ordering Kiosk Market Insights
Self-Ordering Kiosk Market size was valued at USD 2.1 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.3% from 2024 to 2030.

Self-Ordering Kiosk Market Overview
The global self-ordering kiosk market is poised to grow significantly, with an estimated market value of USD 28.5 billion in 2025, driven by increased demand in sectors such as foodservice, retail, and hospitality. The growing focus on contactless ordering systems, enhanced customer experience, and operational efficiency are key factors contributing to this market growth. The expansion of automated solutions is expected to provide strong momentum, further augmented by technological advancements in artificial intelligence (AI) and cloud-based services. The rise of digital transformation in various industries is making self-ordering kiosks an integral part of modern consumer-facing businesses. As of 2025, the market is expected to register a robust CAGR of 16.5% during the forecast period from 2025 to 2030.

