The Asia-Pacific region is expected to exhibit the highest growth due to rapid urbanization and increasing disposable incomes.

9. How are self-ordering kiosks changing the retail industry?
Kiosks improve the shopping experience by allowing customers to browse products, check out quickly, and receive personalized recommendations.

